                              </catchwords>
                           </p>
                        </collation>
                        <condition>
                           <p>Slightly worn-out initial and final. Worm-eaten on the
                              cover. Stitching broken and detached from binding.</p>
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="1" ruledLines="15">
